{"type": "article", "id": 29071, "title": "平衡灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T05:11:01Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607040301424Safm3hG0v1gHeIL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">维也纳的双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.mischertraxler.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mischer’Traxler</a> 把天平和灯具结合在一起，打造出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.mischertraxler.com/projects_equilumen.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Equilumen</a> 的吊灯，希望以此表现平衡性带来的美感。在长棍两侧各安装了一个球形灯，同一个金属圆圈相连。当长棍处于平衡状态时，两边会发出亮度相同的灯光。如果拉动圆圈破坏了平衡，更低一端的灯光会变得明亮而被抬高的灯则会变暗，像是把光传导到了另一侧，很有趣味。Equilumen 曾在今年的米兰设计周上展出，目前还未投入生产。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030347cXtg42MQIGZUDfTl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030405fWr89sCKXaTeBYut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030429Em2FNCGeDnbXg7La.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030457PCkL8039fMDUOJWF.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}